headline.print_headline: Georgian Prosecutors Summon Ex-President Saakashvili for Questioning
headline.main: Georgian Prosecutors Summon Ex-President Saakashvili for Questioning

lead_paragraph: The Georgian prosecutor's office has summoned former president Mikheil Saakashvili for questioning about the poisoning death of a former prime minister and other cases amid a wave of charges and verdicts against former officials.
